{"tid":1025103,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有腰痛巴打 有無斷尾心得？靠拉筋？","createTime":"2019-02-17T05:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T09:35:03.000Z","uid":141793,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"9f7d8776ae8a56bd998f1df7580334e9a756a0b4","tid":1025103,"uid":141793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:54:59.000Z","msg":"想請問各位有腰痛既巴打點搞？<br />\n有無成功例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近呢半年一坐得多就會左邊腰底 突骨個位痛<br />\n<br />\n已經睇過幾個物理冶療都無撚用 跌打都試過<br />\n脊醫無試  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢排睇左youtube 伸展 同 強化core muscle 既片 準備開始試下<br />\n<br />\n有無腰痛巴打自身經驗搞番好？ <br />\n<br />\n同埋聽講坐半個鐘要行一行 同 用左cushion 坐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (呢排好似好啲）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f763f79a03c02da977315fd10aa804cbb384c4e8","tid":1025103,"uid":177089,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"deadlift"},{"pid":"4ae3ae7843aa4b27e8aee9f80b1a73e46491c946","tid":1025103,"uid":28433,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:13:28.000Z","msg":"去照張x光先 之後搵個有料既推拿師傅 搞掂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 椎間盤脫出都醫番"},{"pid":"b3ac29e1867b9c6c5e256f24ddcb8d8d74010565","tid":1025103,"uid":141793,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4ae3ae7843aa4b27e8aee9f80b1a73e46491c946","tid":1025103,"uid":28433,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:13:28.000Z","msg":"去照張x光先 之後搵個有料既推拿師傅 搞掂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 椎間盤脫出都醫番"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:45:23.000Z","msg":"驚會癱 不了"},{"pid":"b8725b50d01d97ce90a612545203dd2b65f00c04","tid":1025103,"uid":28433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3ac29e1867b9c6c5e256f24ddcb8d8